<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ʋno ak kia ʋba yakni ƲIT23</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.8.8.8.) with Refrain 9.8.</time_sig>
<aka>&quot;Will you also go with me to the heavenly country?&quot;</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Iloh itibapishi ma!
 Ʋba yakni achukma ka
 Ia hosh a̱ya li̱ hocha,
 Hʋchi hoyo li fehnʋshke.

[C1]
   Ʋno ak kia ʋba yakni
   Ia lashke, hʋsh ahni cho?

[V2]
 2 Si awant ia pulla cha,
 Nan isht ilaiyukpa hoka
 Hʋsh pisakbano, aiahnit
 Hʋchi̱ hoho̱wa li hoke.

[C2]
   Ʋno ak kia ʋba yakni
   Ia lashke, hʋsh ahni cho?

[V3]
 3 Hatak sipokni̱ chia ma!
 Nitak chilla hi okʋto
 Chim atikonofa hoke;
 Hʋchim ʋlhtaha pullashke.
 CHORUS.
 Ʋno ak kia ʋba yakni
 Ia lashke, hʋsh ahni cho?

[V4]
 4 Hatak himita chia ma!
 Yakni ʋba talaia ka
 Hʋsh ia he tuk pulla ho̱
 Hʋchim anohonli lishke.

[C3]
   Ʋno ak kia ʋba yakni
   Ia lashke, hʋsh ahni cho?

[V5]
 5 Ohoyo chi himita ma!
 Chishno kia chi chu̱kʋsh ma
 Ʋba ish takalechi cha,
 Hʋs siakaiya pullashke.

[C4]
   Ʋno ak kia ʋba yakni
   Ia lashke, hʋsh ahni cho?

[V6]
 6 Ʋlla chipota ʋhleha
 Moma, ʋba Chi̱ki yoka,
 Pit ithanʋt, holitoblit,
 Hʋsh im antia pullashke.

[C5]
   Ʋno ak kia ʋba yakni
   Ia lashke, hʋsh ahni cho?

[V7]
 Hatak hʋsh puta moma ma!
 Himonna 'chʋfa choyuhmit
 Wakayʋt hʋsh ilhkoli cha,
 Ʋba yakni hʋsh iashke.

[C6]
   Hʋchishno mʋt ʋba yakni
   Ona hi a̱ hʋsh ahnashke</lyrics>
<hymn_number>23</hymn_number>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
</song>